WEBVTT

00:12.052 --> 00:13.984
<i>Great, great.</i>

00:14.020 --> 00:15.619
I will have all the Christmas
decorations

00:15.655 --> 00:17.321
in your office
before you know it.

00:17.357 --> 00:18.856
No one is going to recognize
this place

00:18.891 --> 00:20.291
when they come in tomorrow.

00:20.326 --> 00:22.693
Wow. It's gonna be beautiful.

00:22.728 --> 00:25.729
Well, Christmas is kind of
my specialty.

00:25.765 --> 00:27.565
I wish we had known about you
last year.

00:27.600 --> 00:29.467
Oh, I haven't been
in Boston that long.

00:29.502 --> 00:31.802
I moved from Seattle
just after last Christmas

00:31.837 --> 00:34.038
to start my own
interior design company.

00:34.074 --> 00:35.673
That's a long way to come.

00:35.708 --> 00:38.676
Well, that wasn't
the only reason.

00:38.711 --> 00:40.010
Oh, no?

00:40.046 --> 00:41.345
No.

00:41.381 --> 00:43.448
Uh, I found out that I had
family in Vermont.

00:43.483 --> 00:44.582
[ding]

00:46.219 --> 00:48.419
But it wasn't just spending time
with my family

00:48.455 --> 00:50.521
over Christmas that made it
so wonderful.

00:50.557 --> 00:51.889
I met someone.

00:51.958 --> 00:53.491
Someone very special.

00:53.560 --> 00:56.427
Something tells me he felt
the same way about you.

00:56.496 --> 00:58.862
Before I met Ian, I spent most
of my life trying to avoid

00:58.898 --> 01:03.367
the holiday hoopla but he made
me believe in Christmas again.

01:03.436 --> 01:05.303
We had fallen in love
at Christmas

01:05.337 --> 01:07.972
so it just seemed right for us
to get engaged then, too.

01:08.007 --> 01:09.974
He proposed? At Christmas?

01:10.009 --> 01:11.309
Mmmhmm.

01:11.377 --> 01:12.743
That's so romantic.

01:12.778 --> 01:14.878
We rode up on a horse-drawn
carriage to a gazebo

01:14.947 --> 01:16.481
shining with Christmas lights.

01:16.549 --> 01:18.048
So when are you getting married?

01:18.084 --> 01:19.283
Christmas Day.

01:19.319 --> 01:20.751
Oh my gosh, that's perfect.

01:20.786 --> 01:22.686
And the greatest part
of the story

01:22.722 --> 01:24.322
is it's just getting started.

